CheckBoxPreference.android:summary: Displays the game in fullscreen mode. (Requires restart)

ListPreference.android:title: Scaling factor
ListPreference.android:summary: Makes the game view display everything larger.

CheckBoxPreference.android:title: Optimized drawing
CheckBoxPreference.android:summary: Disable this if you see graphical artifacts. Enabling this option will make the game only redraw changed parts of the screen every frame.

CheckBoxPreference.android:title: Confirm rest
CheckBoxPreference.android:summary: Gives a question about whether you want to rest when entering a bed. Otherwise, you will always automatically rest.

CheckBoxPreference.android:title: Confirm attack
CheckBoxPreference.android:summary: "Enables the 'Do you want to attack..?' dialog box when attacking a monster."

ListPreference.android:title: Display monster loot
ListPreference.android:summary: Choose how you want to show the results of a fight to be shown (gold, experience, items).

ListPreference.android:title: Movement method
ListPreference.android:summary: Type of movement method and handling of obstacles.

ListPreference.android:title: Virtual d-pad
ListPreference.android:summary: Enables a virtual on-screen directional pad to guide movement

CheckBoxPreference.android:title: Minimizable d-pad
CheckBoxPreference.android:summary: If the virtual d-pad is enabled, this setting allows the d-pad to be minimized by pressing its center.
